in_3615236\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">März 29, 2023</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104pop1665702622413.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/pop1665702622413.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/pop1665702622413.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"pop1665702622413\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">The trigger name abbreviation. </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"pop1665702622413__topic_d93896e1_d93897e1_d93898e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"pop1665702622413__p_d93899e1_d93900e1_d93901e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">&lt;$triggerAbbr&gt;</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"pop1665702622413__p_d93902e1_d93903e1_d93904e1\"><span class=\"keyword cmdname\">#define</span>\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">&lt;$triggerAbbr&gt;</span>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Value</var>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"pop1665702622413__section_bjy_qj3_lwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d566705e77\">Scope</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"pop1665702622413__p_d93908e1_d93909e1_d93910e1\">Trigger or container, depending on where the constant\n            is defined. By default, <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">&lt;$triggerAbbr&gt;</span> has container scope.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"pop1665702622413__section_uhd_jk3_lwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d566705e89\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"pop1665702622413__p_d93914e1_d93915e1_d93916e1\">You can explicitly define an abbreviation, or any\n            other string, to identify a particular trigger. If you do so, you must also explicitly\n            define the scope using <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">#startdefine</span> and\n            <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">#enddefine</span>. For example:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"pop1665702622413__pre_cvb_sk3_lwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">#startdefine\n#define $triggerAbbr=Detail\ntrigger detail\n ...\nend\n#enddefine\n</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"pop1665702622413__p_d93917e1_d93918e1_d93919e1\">If not explicitly defined,\n               <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">&lt;$triggerAbbr&gt;</span> returns the following abbreviations:</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"pop1665702622413__table_d10310e1_d10311e1_d10312e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Trigger and Component Name Abbreviations</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"pop1665702622413__table_d10310e1_d10311e1_d10312e1__entry__1\">Abbreviation</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"pop1665702622413__table_d10310e1_d10311e1_d10312e1__entry__2\">Trigger or Container</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"pop1665702622413__table_d10310e1_d10311e1_d10312e1__entry__3\">Object Type</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"pop1665702622413__table_d10310e1_d10311e1_d10312e1__entry__1\">ASCR </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"pop1665702622413__table_d10310e1_d10311e1_d10312e1__entry__2\">USCRIPT </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"pop1665702622413__table_d10310e1_d10311e1_d10312e1__entry__3\">Application shell </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"pop1665702622413__table_d10310e1_d10311e1_d10312e1__entry__1\">CSCR </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"pop1665702622413__table_d10310e1_d10311e1_d10312e1__entry__2\">USCRIPT </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"pop1665702622413__table_d10310e1_d10311e1_d10312e1__entry__3\">Component </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"pop1665702622413__table_d10310e1_d10311e1_d10312e1__entry__1\">DCLA </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"pop1665702622413__table_d10310e1_d10311e1_d10312e1__entry__2\">UDECLARATIONS </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"pop1665702622413__table_d10310e1_d10311e1_d10312e1__entry__3\">Application shell </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"pop1665702622413__table_d10310e1_d10311e1_d10312e1__entry__1\">DCLC </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"pop1665702622413__table_d10310e1_d10311e1_d10312e1__entry__2\">UDECLARATIONS </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"pop1665702622413__table_d10310e1_d10311e1_d10312e1__entry__3\">Component </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"pop1665702622413__table_d10310e1_d10311e1_d10312e1__entry__1\">DCLE </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"pop1665702622413__table_d10310e1_d10311e1_d10312e1__entry__2\">UDECLARATIONS </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"pop1665702622413__table_d10310e1_d10311e1_d10312e1__entry__3\">Entity</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"pop1665702622413__table_d10310e1_d10311e1_d10312e1__entry__1\">DCLF </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"pop1665702622413__table_d10310e1_d10311e1_d10312e1__entry__2\">UDECLARATIONS </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"pop1665702622413__table_d10310e1_d10311e1_d10312e1__entry__3\">Field </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"pop1665702622413__table_d10310e1_d10311e1_d10312e1__entry__1\">ESCR </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"pop1665702622413__table_d10310e1_d10311e1_d10312e1__entry__2\">UCOLL_SCRIPT </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"pop1665702622413__table_d10310e1_d10311e1_d10312e1__entry__3\">Entity </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"pop1665702622413__table_d10310e1_d10311e1_d10312e1__entry__1\">FSCR </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"pop1665702622413__table_d10310e1_d10311e1_d10312e1__entry__2\">USCRIPT </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"pop1665702622413__table_d10310e1_d10311e1_d10312e1__entry__3\">Field </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"pop1665702622413__table_d10310e1_d10311e1_d10312e1__entry__1\">OSCR </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"pop1665702622413__table_d10310e1_d10311e1_d10312e1__entry__2\">UOCC_SCRIPT </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"pop1665702622413__table_d10310e1_d10311e1_d10312e1__entry__3\">Entity </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"pop1665702622413__table_d10310e1_d10311e1_d10312e1__entry__1\">OPTN </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"pop1665702622413__table_d10310e1_d10311e1_d10312e1__entry__2\">option </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"pop1665702622413__table_d10310e1_d10311e1_d10312e1__entry__3\">Menu Item </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"pop1665702622413__table_d10310e1_d10311e1_d10312e1__entry__1\">PDIS </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"pop1665702622413__table_d10310e1_d10311e1_d10312e1__entry__2\">preDisplay </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"pop1665702622413__table_d10310e1_d10311e1_d10312e1__entry__3\">Menu </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"pop1665702622413__p_d93920e1_d93921e1_d93922e1\">If you migrated from Uniface 9, trigger abbreviations\n            might be explicitly defined. For more information, see <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ydz1665702744762.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ydz1665702744762.html\" title=\"Prior to Uniface 10, most triggers were defined in their own container and the name of this container could be accessed using the &lt;$triggerAbbr&gt; precompiler constant.\">Migrated Trigger Abbreviations</a>.</p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ots1665702620497.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>#define</a><p>Define a constant name and value.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/unu1665702620895.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>#startdefine</a><p>Declares the scope of precompiler constant declarations (#define's)</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/rmq1665702620822.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>#enddefine</a><p>Declares the end scope of precompiler constants declared after the corresponding #startdefine.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3615236\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3615236\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "<$triggerAbbr> Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated März 29, 2023 Summarize Uniface 10.4 The trigger name abbreviation. <$triggerAbbr> #define <$triggerAbbr> = Value Scope Trigger or container, depending on where the constant is defined. By default, <$triggerAbbr> has container scope. Description You can explicitly define an abbreviation, or any other string, to identify a particular trigger. If you do so, you must also explicitly define the scope using #startdefine and #enddefine . For example: #startdefine #define $triggerAbbr=Detail trigger detail ... end #enddefine Copy If not explicitly defined, <$triggerAbbr> returns the following abbreviations: Table 1. Trigger and Component Name Abbreviations Abbreviation Trigger or Container Object Type ASCR USCRIPT Application shell CSCR USCRIPT Component DCLA UDECLARATIONS Application shell DCLC UDECLARATIONS Component DCLE UDECLARATIONS Entity DCLF UDECLARATIONS Field ESCR UCOLL_SCRIPT Entity FSCR USCRIPT Field OSCR UOCC_SCRIPT Entity OPTN option Menu Item PDIS preDisplay Menu If you migrated from Uniface 9, trigger abbreviations might be explicitly defined. For more information, see Migrated Trigger Abbreviations . Related Links #define Define a constant name and value. #startdefine Declares the scope of precompiler constant declarations (#define's) #enddefine Declares the end scope of precompiler constants declared after the corresponding #startdefine. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}